OL,5,G2300 The X-Files
OL,6,     FWhen a frozen alien corpse is
OL,7,     Fdiscovered in Canada, Mulder is
OL,8,     Fconvinced that it will finally
OL,9,     Fprovide the hard evidence he has
OL,10,     Fbeen looking for.
OL,11,G0000 Shoplifters: Caught Red Handed
OL,12,     FIn a sports store, a woman
OL,13,     Fprotests that she's paid for all
OL,14,     Fher items, but her receipts tell a
OL,15,     Fdifferent story. Plus undercover
OL,16,     Fdetective Steve monitors pick
OL,17,     Fpocketing in China Town. (Ep16)
